<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_558" id="278r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_558_r1l16"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu heydeck </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_558_r1l17">Edler lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Vns haben dıe <expan>vvolgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_558_r1l18">vnd <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>Graf<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Swarcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu <expan>Leẅchtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_558_r1l19">brief geſandt . eẅr edel etwas . antreffend . VVolten wır niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_558_r1l20"><expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . wır <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell . <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_558_r1l21"><expan>ſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> in gut daʒ ſıch eẅr edel deſt bas wıſſ in den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_558_r1l22">ʒu <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_558_r1l23"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_558" id="278r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Heydeck
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler, lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns haben die
                                <expan>wolgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Swarczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        zu <expan>Lewchtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brief
                        gesandt, ewr edel etwas antreffend; wolten wir niht
                            <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, wir <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> ein <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan> ver<expan>sloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> in gut, daz sich ewr edel dest bas wiss in
                        den <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn
                        wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
